## Instructions

Address the issues identified in the review report.

### Process

1. Read `agent-review-report.md` from the change directory (`{{task.changePath}}`)
2. Address each issue systematically, starting with highest severity
3. Verify each fix resolves the issue
4. Run tests after fixes to ensure no regressions

### Fix Guidelines

- Make minimal, focused changes to address each issue
- Do not introduce new features or refactoring beyond what's needed
- Ensure fixes don't break existing functionality
- Update tests if needed to cover the fixes

### Signal

When all issues have been addressed:
```
<aop>FIX_COMPLETE</aop>
```

If unable to fix an issue, document the blocker clearly before signaling.
